result.title: Cannot see standings after cloning a contest
result.content:
Hello,

I have tried cloning a previous codeforces contest to hold a private contest but I cannot access the standings, I get the Error page("All your bugs are belong to me."). The standings are available if I create a mashup and add problems one by one. Is this a "feature" of cloning the contests or is this a bug?

P.S. I am sorry if this has been asked before, I tried to google but couldn't find any results.

UPDATE: Just noticed that even problemset page and contest pages give the same error. But the problem with cloning contests isn't related to this because I have experienced it quite some time ago(Last week to be exact), and it still persists.
